The Amulet
 



Introducing the Allergy Amulet: a rapid, portable, food allergen & ingredient detection device.










Why?
 
Restaurants are responsible for over half of all food allergy fatalities. This is a statistic we are trying to change.






Why?
 
Restaurants are responsible for over half of all food allergy fatalities. This is a statistic we are trying to change.


 How it works: Users insert the disposable test strip into their food and within secondsthe reader alerts users to the presence or absence of target allergens/ingredients. 


















Ways to Wear
 
Most allergic reactions occur outside the home. So we married function with fashion. 






Ways to Wear
 
Most allergic reactions occur outside the home. So we married function with fashion. 





















