allergy amulet inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Retail - Discretionary
Sub-Industry: Consumer Elec & Applc Stores
Allergy Amulet, Inc. manufactures food allergen detection devices. The Company offers a portable device that alerts users to the presence and absence of target allergens. Allergy Amulet serves customers in the United States.




Corporate Information
Address:

111 North Fairchild Street
Suite 240
Madison, WI 53703
United States


